Type Alias# sec_protocol_pre_shared_key_selection_t

iOS 2.0+iPadOS 2.0+Mac Catalyst 13.0+macOS 10.0+tvOS 9.0+visionOS 1.0+watchOS 2.0+

```
typealias sec_protocol_pre_shared_key_selection_t = (
    sec_protocol_metadata_t, dispatch_data_t?,
    @escaping sec_protocol_pre_shared_key_selection_complete_t
) -> Void
```

## [ Parameters ](/documentation/security/sec_protocol_pre_shared_key_selection_t#parameters)

`metadata`A `sec_protocol_metadata_t` instance.

`psk_identity_hint`A `dispatch_data_t` object carrying the peer’s (optional) PSK identity hint.

`complete`A `sec_protocol_pre_shared_key_selection_complete_t` block to be invoked when PSK selection is complete.

## [Discussion](/documentation/security/sec_protocol_pre_shared_key_selection_t#discussion)

Block to be invoked when the client must choose a PSK identity given a hint from its peer.
